text: Masilo Ramothata (born 30 November 1989) is a South African cricketer. He made his first-class debut for Griqualand West in the 2014–15 Sunfoil 3-Day Cup on 11 December 2014. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:South African cricketers Category:Gauteng cricketers Category:Griqualand West cricketers Category:Cricketers from Johannesburg
